Outgrow is an Easy & Intuitive App made in 6 Languages that help us connect with the Indian farmers locally across the 5 States viz. Karnataka, Tamil Nadu, Andhra Pradesh, Telangana & Maharashtra. With a host of services like, Automated Soil Labs, Microclimatic Weather, Artificial Intelligence, Regenerative Farming & a larger Farmer Service Network, this app will aid farmers to improve their productivity & reduce losses in the crop lifecycle management. We are in the pursuit of revolutionizing the agricultural landscape in India.
